data.description: Discover this spacious tri-level home in New Carlisle, part of the New Prairie United School Corporation (Olive Elementary). Recently reduced in price, this home offers 4 bedrooms and 1 FULL bathroom (with HEATED FLOORS) on the upper level, providing ample space for everyone. The main level boasts a welcoming living room, a perfect-for-gatherings dining room, and a spacious kitchen.  The lower level you'll find ANOTHER FULL bathroom, a cozy living room with a gas fireplace for chilly evenings, a convenient wet bar for entertaining, and a utility/laundry room. Outside, the fenced-in backyard and two sheds cater to your storage needs, while the large front yard welcomes you home.  Take advantage of the proximity to the charming town, filled with hidden treasures like specialty shops, restaurants & recreational opportunities. This home offers a perfect blend of comfort & style. Act now to make it YOURS!
